   A privileged location in the heart of
   the capital of the Dukes of Burgundy

4-star Hotel Dijon Centre

   5, Rue Michelet - BP 52408 - 21024 Dijon
   P. +33380508888
   contact@chapeau-rouge.fr

   L'hostellerie du Chapeau Rouge
   L’Hostellerie du Chapeau Rouge welcomes you to Burgundy, in the heart
   of the historic centre of Dijon, listed as a UNESCO world heritage
   site, only 15 minutes away from the famous Route des Grands Crus, with
   its outstanding vineyards known as "Climats de Bourgogne", also on the
   UNESCO World Heritage list.

   Restaurant William Frachot

   2 stars in the 2019 MICHELIN® guide
   The William Frachot Restaurant welcomes you from Tuesday to Saturday,
   for lunch or dinner.
   Adjacent lounge available for private events. Booking advised.

   Services
   SERVICES & AMENITIES

     * Valet-porter service
     * Free Wi-Fi throughout the establishment
     * Reception: 24/7
     * Pets are not allowed(except guide dogs)

   SERVICES

     * 4-star hotel
     * William Frachot Restaurant: 2 stars in the 2019 MICHELIN® guide
     * Wellbeing area open to hotel guests and outside customers
     * Bar

   Comfortable bed Hotel de charme Dijon

   Discover Dijon
   Located less than 5 minutes away on foot from the train station, tram,
   buses and Place Darcy, and 300 metres away from a secure car park, the
   hotel is only a 15-minute drive from the Dijon-Bourgogne airport.
   An ideal location for a sightseeing holiday or a business trip.

